extendedInfo.description: MyCCC Mobile provides up to the minute information to the students, faculty, staff and alumni of Coastline College.Version 1.0 of MyCCC Mobile includes:MyBill: Provides current enrollment, billing and registration information.Schedule: Browse the class schedule, view class times, locations and more.Map: Find your location and search for specific buildings.Events: The latest events around campus.Contacts: find contact information for faculty, staff or administrators.Emergency: find campus emergency contact information.

reviews.title: Could be improved but not bad
reviews.comment: Can lag, but not a bad app has useful items. It would be even more useful though if this app would also connect to your cccd email!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: It\'s okay for an iOS port...
reviews.comment: It\'s pretty useful, good for getting news and looking up classes. But the design needs work. This is Android you\'re coding for, there\'s no need for a back button or a menu button on screen.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Needs inprovment
reviews.comment: Works okay, however it lags a little. Displays schedule and your fees well, would recommend for coastline cc students. Thanks cccd!
reviews.author: A Google User
